":"The talk will go into the \"Ship It?\" culture that's a big part of GitHub.  How we use the git scm to help us deploy features fast and respond to problems on the site in a timely fashion.","code":"16M04","id":15,"kind":"session","position":1,"title":"Shipping at the Speed of Life","title_en":"Shipping at the Speed of Life","speakers":[{"abstract":"Hacker at GitHub","abstract_en":"Hacker at GitHub","code":"16M04:1","id":7,"name":"Corey Donohoe","name_en":"Corey Donohoe","organizations":[{"code":null,"created_at":"2013-04-23T11:52:44Z","id":6,"name":"GitHub","name_en":null,"updated_at":"2013-04-23T11:52:44Z"}]}],"sessions":[]}]},{"created_at":"2013-04-23T11:52:44Z","end_at":"2011-07-16T07:10:00Z","id":13,"place_area_id":2,"start_at":"2011-07-16T06:40:00Z","updated_at":"2013-04-23T11:52:44Z","sessions":[{"abstract":null,"abstract_en":null,"code":"2011-07-16:M:break:2","id":17,"kind":"break","position":1,"title":"\u4f11\u61a9","title_en":"Break","speakers":[],"sessions":[]}]},{"created_at":"2013-04-23T11:52:45Z","end_at":"2011-07-16T08:10:00Z","id":15,"place_area_id":2,"start_at":"2011-07-16T07:10:00Z","updated_at":"2013-04-23T11:52:45Z","sessions":[{"abstract":"Modern large scale applications often benefit from being composed of multiple smaller applications.  This can provide many benefits, but it can often make testing each piece more complex. I will cover a technique we use at Engine Yard to easily test these pieces individually and as a piece of the whole. ","abstract_en":"Modern large scale applications often benefit from being composed of multiple smaller applications.  This can provide many benefits, but it can often make testing each piece more complex. I will cover a technique we use at Engine Yard to easily test these pieces individually and as a piece of the whole. ","code":"16M05","id":20,"kind":"session","position":1,"title":"Toggleable Mocks and Testing Strategies in a Service Oriented Architecture","title_en":"Toggleable Mocks and Testing Strategies 